54:["$","h3",null,{"id":"远离一线项目技术会不会退化","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"远离一线项目，技术会不会退化？"}]
55:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"培训逼着自己去梳理总结自己的知识体系，达到教学相长，当然也就失去了置身一线的机会。在传播分享的同时要不断地学习操练，还可以回归一线去实战。而在TW，这样的机会随时都存在。"}]
56:["$","hr",null,{"className":"my-8 border-border"}]
57:["$","h2",null,{"id":"培训中的收获","className":"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3 scroll-mt-24","children":"培训中的收获"}]
58:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["我刚加入TW培训团队，仝老师就让我接管了NHO的课程体系建立",["$","a",null,{"href":"#note-6","className":"text-primary hover:underline break-all","children":"[6]"}],"，恰逢NHO的改革期，历时三个月改革初级阶段基本成型，这个过程打开我的另一扇小窗，比如，沟通协作、知识体系化、外训讲师、认证机会等。"]}]
59:["$","h3",null,{"id":"强化沟通协作","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"强化沟通协作"}]
5a:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"身为一名言语不多的程序员，我的沟通神经长时间没有得到足够的训练，自然不甚敏感。所以在接管NHO课程体系建立之后，除了课程设计和课程落地，我还要跟People团队不同角色去沟通，逼着自己跳出舒适区。另外，改革前期，在推动讲师赋能上的难题上，频繁地跟People去协作探讨解决方案，推动NHO改革的落地。高频率的沟通，让我变得习惯和享受沟通过程。当然，TW的小伙伴沟通协作上也很友好。"}]
5b:["$","h3",null,{"id":"梳理知识体系","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"梳理知识体系"}]
5c:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"在培训期间，我觉得收获最大的是知识梳理。我需要将课程结合业务方（客户）的目标设计出来，然后通过不断讲授和反馈来迭代课程。这个过程我一直在梳理零散的知识，不断建立知识的关联性，从而形成特定的知识体系。将知识进行传授分享，收集反馈并不断完善，成长最多的是自己，这就是所谓的教学相长。"}]
5d:["$","h3",null,{"id":"拓展外训视野","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"拓展外训视野"}]
5e:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["TW咨询团队会承接一些培训的项目，作为培训团队的一员，可以有更多地机会到外训战场去见识行业的面貌。因为外训天然具有内训无法比拟的压力，它能很好地锻炼你的心理素质，同时，更重要的是看到行业的一些真实状况，你可能会发现行业存在不少休克鱼",["$","a",null,{"href":"#note-7","className":"text-primary hover:underline break-all","children":"[7]"}],"，从而触发你更多的思考。"]}]
5f:["$","h3",null,{"id":"获得认证机会","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"获得认证机会"}]
60:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"TW正在举办一场将可能轰动行业的认证项目，而作为培训团队一员，通过前期积累了更多的实战教学经验，能够参与到前期认证体系建设团队中贡献力量的同事还能跟咨询大牛学习，这是一次难得的成长机会之一。"}]
61:["$","hr",null,{"className":"my-8 border-border"}]
62:["$","h2",null,{"id":"培训中的困惑","className":"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3 scroll-mt-24","children":"培训中的困惑"}]
63:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"当然在培训中，看到了不一样风景，也听到了不一样的言论，从而产生了一些困惑。比如，作为培训师，如何看待培训无用论？输出居多的情况下如何保证输入？如何让自己更加专业？"}]
64:["$","h3",null,{"id":"如何看待培训无用论","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"如何看待培训无用论？"}]
65:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"最开始听到培训无用论，我似乎有些沮丧到怀疑人生。竟然培训无用，那公司为什么还花那么多的投资在培训上？通过跟前辈交流，不断的参加不同种类的培训，对这句话有了更深入的理解。"}]
66:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["培训确实",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"\"无用\""}],"，举个例子，知识焦虑让很多人去买了付费知识，并投入时间学习知识，遗憾的是，不少人忽略了后期的持续学习和刻意练习，最终没能将知识转化成自己的技能，从而进一步加深了知识焦虑。"]}]
67:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"培训的一大核心作用是，让你知道自己不知道，并配合知识扩充、实战操练和技能转化三个阶段来达到提升的目的。而一位优秀的培训师会将这些融合到他课程体系中。"}]
68:["$","h3",null,{"id":"如何保证持续的输入","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"如何保证持续的输入？"}]
69:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"培训做多了，尤其是重复相同的培训，如何保证新鲜有效的输入也是培训师需要面对的一个问题。答案很确定 -- 持续学习。而模糊的是如何持续学习？自学 + 实战两项能够经常得到练习，导师指导和业界培训这两项却起到至关重要的画龙点睛作用。在这方面，TW能力建设团队现在支持团队成员报名参加业界专项培训进行个人能力的提升。"}]
6a:["$","hr",null,{"className":"my-8 border-border"}]
6b:["$","h2",null,{"id":"未来的路","className":"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3 scroll-mt-24","children":"未来的路"}]
6c:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"在过去6个月时间，从写代码到做培训，跟HRBP团队协作将建立NHO体系。我对未来的路我也不是非常明晰，后面也许还会不断地产生新的困惑，也会不断得到答案。"}]
6d:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"因为个人意愿加入了培训的队伍，所以要好好做培训，因为要更好地做培训，所以要让自己不断地输入。在TW这个充满机会的组织，我目前想到了三个方向："}]
6e:["$","ol",null,{"className":"list-decimal list-outside pl-5 my-4 space-y-2","children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":"走向专业培训师之路，匍匐前行，建功立业"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":"回归交付团队，高效战斗，Coach团队"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":"迈入咨询团队，大刀阔斧，Coach客户"}],"\n"]}]
6f:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"三个方向并不非相互独立，它们或许相辅相成，而重要的是你能不能在你感兴趣的领域取持续取得进步，去影响更多的人。"}]
70:["$","hr",null,{"className":"my-8 border-border"}]
71:["$","h2",null,{"id":"注释","className":"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3 scroll-mt-24","children":"注释"}]
72:["$","a",null,{"id":"note-1"}]
73:["$","ol",null,{"className":"list-decimal list-outside pl-5 my-4 space-y-2","children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"TW中的师徒制的形式有两种，一种是转正前会有一个Buddy带你快速成长，转正后会有一个Sponsor在你职业生涯中帮助你成长。"}],"\n",["$","a",null,{"id":"note-2"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":[["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"发展他人的意愿"}],"被TW能力建设团队列为招聘的首要要求，其他还包括：",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"自学能力"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"开发心态"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"有效沟通"}]]}],"\n",["$","a",null,{"id":"note-3"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"TW仝键是一位很资深的咨询师和培训师，带领了团队建立了培训体系，现加入外训咨询团队，内训由人称大姐大的资深咨询师禚娴静带头。"}],"\n",["$","a",null,{"id":"note-4"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["应届生培训的经历请参阅 ",["$","a",null,{"href":"","className":"text-primary hover:underline break-all","children":"ThoughtWorks给你不一样的入职之旅"}]]}],"\n",["$","a",null,{"id":"note-5"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["成年人学习的四个阶段：",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"体验"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"反思"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"抽象"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"行动"}],"，讲师的首要职责是引导学员通过体验促发思考，经历了一定的思考之后进行总结提炼，最后进行落地。"]}],"\n",["$","a",null,{"id":"note-6"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"NHO，为期三天的新员工入职培训，由TW文化方面和敏捷项目体验组成。"}],"\n",["$","a",null,{"id":"note-7"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"my-1 break-words pl-1","children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"休克鱼，企业投资与经营管理领域的概念，指硬件设施好，但管理不善的企业。本文泛指管理和文化理念僵化、不思变革的组织，以及组织中不思进取的员工。"}],"\n"]}],"\n"]}]
